        "title": "Exclamations: voi että, no voi vitsi",
        "summary": "The family-friendly end of Finnish exclamations: voi että (oh my), no voi vitsi (oh man), herranjestas (good heavens), huhhuh (phew), no johan nyt jotain (well I never). They carry the emotion so your sentence doesn't have to.",
